snippet.title: DISSIDIA 012[duodecim] FINAL FANTASY Final Trailer: English Version
snippet.description:
The final Japanese trailer for DISSIDA 012[duodecim] FINAL FANTASY, exclusively for the PSP® (PlayStation®Portable) system! Available 3/22/11. Visit http://na.square-enix.com/dissidia_012 for more information.

ESRB Rating: Teen with Fantasy Violence, Mild Language, Partial Nudity, Suggestive Themes
